                        <head>51. Summary of Conclusions of a Meeting of the Senior Review
                                Group<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d51fn1">Source: National
                                Archives, <persName corresp="#p_NRM1">Nixon</persName> Presidential
                                Materials, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (H-Files), Box
                                H–111, Senior Review Group Meetings Minutes, Originals, 1970. Top
                                Secret; <gloss target="#t_Nodis1">Nodis</gloss>. The meeting took
                                place in the Situation Room of the White House.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" from="1970-10-16T16:03:00-04:00" to="1970-10-16T16:47:00-04:00">October 16, 1970, 4:03–4:47 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline></opener>
                        <list type="subject">
                            <head>SUBJECT</head>
                            <item>Cambodia—<gloss target="#t_NSSM1">NSSM</gloss> 99 (Part I)</item>
                        </list>
